        <!-- Version 6.2.2 - Security Fixes & Bug Fixes -->
        <item>
            <title>Version 6.2.2</title>
            <link>https://github.com/cmdlabtech/AIO-SSL-Tool/releases/tag/V6.2.2</link>
            <sparkle:version>12</sparkle:version>
            <sparkle:shortVersionString>6.2.2</sparkle:shortVersionString>
            <description><![CDATA[
                <h2>What's New in 6.2.2</h2>
                <ul>
                    <li>Security: DN field escaping to prevent OpenSSL -subj injection</li>
                    <li>Security: Private key encryption now uses file-based password passing (no longer exposed in process args)</li>
                    <li>Security: Consistent 0600 permissions on all temporary key and cert files</li>
                    <li>Security: Windows private key files now restricted to current user via icacls</li>
                    <li>Bug fix: Removed duplicate function definition and dead code in Windows app</li>
                    <li>Bug fix: Chain building loop now has a max depth limit of 15</li>
                    <li>Bug fix: Bare exception handlers replaced with specific types throughout Windows app</li>
                    <li>Windows: PFX advanced options now clearly note they are informational on Windows</li>
                </ul>
            ]]></description>
            <pubDate>Sat, 07 Mar 2026 12:00:00 +0000</pubDate>
            <enclosure
                url="https://github.com/cmdlabtech/AIO-SSL-Tool/releases/download/V6.2.2/AIO-SSL-Tool-macOS-V6.2.2.dmg"
